Global Positioning System (GPS) application entry point.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: Global Positioning System Task application entry point. This function performs app initialization, then waits for the cFE ES Startup Sync, then executes the main processing loop.

simplesect.title: Assumptions, External Events, and Notes:
simplesect.para: If there is an unrecoverable failure during initialization the main loop is never executed and the application will exit.

briefdescription.para: Initialize the Global Positioning System (GPS) application.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: Global Positioning System application initialization routine. This function performs all the required startup steps to initialize (or restore from CDS) GPS data structures and get the application registered with the cFE services so it can begin to receive command messages and send events.

simplesect.title: Assumptions, External Events, and Notes:
simplesect.para: None

briefdescription.para: Receive and process messages from the scheduler pipe.
